<a href="/questions/181895-i-would-like-to-know-what-source-of-hard">I would like to know what source of hard facts were used to create the basis of this book.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_181895'><a id="like_count_community_question_181895" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/181895?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F93426.Genghis_Khan_and_the_Making_of_the_Modern_World">like</a></span>

