      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2468245-genghis-khan-and-the-making-of-the-modern-world">Quotes from Genghis Khan and ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;The first key to leadership is self-control.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/337954-the-first-key-to-leadership-is-self-control">57 likes</a>
            </nobr>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;If you can't swallow your pride, you can't lead. Even the highest mountain had animals that step on it.&rdquo;</span>
